# Copy this to .env (or export these directly) before running main.py
#
# Get a key at https://console.cloud.google.com/ -- enable the "Places API (New)"
# on the project, then create an API key. Restrict it to that API and (in
# production) to your server's IP, or the Application Restrictions a server-side
# key supports. Do NOT use a browser-restricted key for this -- this script
# calls the API server-side.
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_key_here
